@baseUrl = http://localhost:3100
@staffRole = STAFF
@storeId = REPLACE_WITH_LOCATION_ID

### Sales history default page (STAFF+, completed/finalised sales only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sales/history
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}

### Sales history search by order number, customer, or staff (STAFF+)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sales/history?q=eric
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}

### Sales history filtered by status and date range (STAFF+)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sales/history?status=complete&dateFrom=2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z&dateTo=2026-04-05T23:59:59.999Z
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}

### Sales history including drafts explicitly (STAFF+)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sales/history?status=draft,complete
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}

### Sales history filtered to one store with pagination (STAFF+)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sales/history?storeId={{storeId}}&page=2&pageSize=20
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
